item.title: CVE-2023-32113|2024-03-12T21:51:09.272Z -- sap_se -- sap%20gui%20for%20windows
item.description: SAP GUI for Windows - version 7.70, 8.0, allows an unauthorized attacker to gain NTLM authentication information of a victim by tricking it into clicking a prepared shortcut file. Depending on the authorizations of the victim, the attacker can read and modify potentially sensitive information after successful exploitation.
